  "3185770": {
    "name": "Native Isekai Defense",
    "steam_appid": 3185770,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《原生异世界防御》发生在一个名为鲁米纳的世界。几百年前，自称为“始祖”的人登上了世界的舞台。他们指挥着怪物军队，将鲁米纳的世界卷入了一场无尽的大战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >几个世纪过去了，始祖和他们的怪物军队成功征服并污染了世界的三分之一。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，希望尚未破灭。天才炼金术士阿里尔成功创造了“虚灵连接点”，这是一种能够净化被怪物污染的鲁米纳土地的神器。随着这一发明，反击的时刻已经到来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >于是，“伊甸计划”启动了。先锋小队被组建起来，前去夺回被污染的土地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >先锋小队  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和其他玩家一起加入先锋小队，成为鲁米纳的精英战士吧！从各种角色中组建队伍，一起挑战各种任务！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/2e9fda71865996148dbb584c2a8b0c84.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/2e9fda71865996148dbb584c2a8b0c84.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/2e9fda71865996148dbb584c2a8b0c84.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >伊甸计划  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夺回鲁米纳土地的时刻到了！前往污染的土地，激活虚灵连接点，然后保护它免受怪物攻击，直到土地完全净化为止！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/20b194fbd79c4720ee7396eafb72adaf.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/20b194fbd79c4720ee7396eafb72adaf.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/20b194fbd79c4720ee7396eafb72adaf.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >构建完美防御！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造路障和塔楼来帮助保护以太核心！打造敌人无法突破的终极防线！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你的催化剂！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每波结束时使用随机催化剂强化你的角色！选择适合你游戏风格的催化剂组合，保护以太核心直到最后一滴血。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/dc2f36cdf24395d66b3e804b38cce501.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/dc2f36cdf24395d66b3e804b38cce501.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/dc2f36cdf24395d66b3e804b38cce501.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小心误伤队友！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意你的每一个动作！看看四周——你的队友在附近吗？确保不要伤害他们！但如果真的发生了，记住，这是战争！误伤队友是无法避免的！没有牺牲就没有战争！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/a64638793ce49d471800fe882c64da6f.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/a64638793ce49d471800fe882c64da6f.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/a64638793ce49d471800fe882c64da6f.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成为英雄！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每一个任务中，你将冲进敌人占领的领土！运用你的技能和武器，和队友并肩作战！用你的生命，或者队友的生命来保护虚灵连接点！活下来，夺回我们的土地！成为鲁米纳的英雄吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/642e1049fcef22e38318b63bc5234ce0.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/642e1049fcef22e38318b63bc5234ce0.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/642e1049fcef22e38318b63bc5234ce0.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >怪物的浪潮！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无尽的怪物袭击！还有一个巨大的头目？！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即便如此，你也必须活下来！即使这意味着踩着你同伴的生命前进！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了未来！让我们从他们肮脏的手中夺回并解放我们的土地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/870a6278621f8960931ca6fa37070ed1.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/870a6278621f8960931ca6fa37070ed1.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/870a6278621f8960931ca6fa37070ed1.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
